data.description: Beautiful Eagleridge Two Story. Located in the heart of Northside Pueblo this home hosts 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 1,718 square feet on a corner lot.  The front yard has a large lawn and mature shrubs and the fully fenced backyard is completely xeriscaped. As you enter the home you will be greeted by the open kitchen, living room and dining room. The main level has its own half bath making it perfect for entertaining guests. On the upper level you have all three bedrooms with the additional two bathrooms and an upstairs laundry room. The primary bedroom is large with a walk-in closet and has lots of natural light from its south facing windows. The attached primary bathroom has a dual vanity sink, soaking tub and walk in shower. This home is close to all the amenities Eagleridge has to offer, dining, shopping and quick access to Interstate 25. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours.
